# Lattice (Absynth) — Project Rules

## What This Is

Lattice is a semi-modular VST3/AU synthesizer plugin. It consists of two separate GitHub repos that are developed together locally:

- **absynth-ui** (`ui` remote) — Vue 3 + Vite web-based UI. Lives at the repo root alongside `package.json`.
- **absynth-vst** (`vst` remote) — C++ JUCE plugin engine. Lives at `absynth-vst/` as a subdirectory.

The UI is embedded in the JUCE plugin via `juce::WebBrowserComponent`. Communication between the C++ audio engine and the Vue UI uses the **JUCE WebBridge** (`juce-framework-frontend` npm package, resolved from `./absynth-vst/JUCE/modules/juce_gui_extra/native/javascript`).

